---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — DeveX Tools" description="Learn about DeveX Tools — who we are, how we test developer tools, and why our reviews are independent.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 32px; max-width: 740px; margin: 40px auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">About DeveX Tools</h1>
    
    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <strong>DeveX Tools</strong> is an independent developer tool review platform. 
        We test and evaluate IDEs, CI/CD platforms, version control systems, API tools, 
        and every other piece of software that crosses a developer's desk.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Founded in 2024, DeveX Tools was born from a simple frustration: most "developer tool reviews" 
        are either marketing fluff paid for by vendors, or shallow listicles written by people 
        who don't actually write code. We decided to do it differently — every review on this site 
        is written by a practicing engineer who has used the tool in a real production environment.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Our team is small (<strong>6 engineers</strong> across time zones), which means every review 
        is meaningful. We don't chase volume — we chase depth. Each review includes hands-on testing, 
        quantitative benchmarks where applicable, and honest pros/cons based on real engineering tradeoffs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Our Review Philosophy</h2>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>No sponsored placements.</strong> Zero. Tools earn their spot on our lists based on merit, not marketing budget.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Real engineering context.</strong> We test tools in CI/CD pipelines, under load, and in team workflows — not just in a sandbox.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Transparent scoring.</strong> Every score comes with a breakdown so you can weigh what matters to your team.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Living reviews.</strong> We update reviews as tools evolve. A review from 2024 may have a 2026 addendum.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Contact</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        Questions, suggestions, or tool recommendations? 
        Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@devex-tools.net">hello@devex-tools.net</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
